leve.name: You're a Liar, Mansel Black
leve.description: Twin-tongued Mansel, the dark thaumaturge of the Lambs of Dalamud, has finally surfaced. He has no doubt suffered privations during these months on the run; malice fattens upon lean times, they say. Tread carefully and strike surely, for fat or lean, there is no ferity greater than that of a cornered beast.
